name: "Very Messy Thoughts" by RFY (HF) & FEH (TT)
description: [Crayon on notebook page with digital embellishments.] Here we see the intrepid artists trying out some concepts in sketch form. I like were this is heading... The MOOD is perfection. (Thank goodness the kid hasn't gotten tired of coloring with grandpa yet!) ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool) & Felicity Echo Hanson (Toddler Terror)
